Infrastructure Layer:
VPC Architecture:

Created production VPC (dipesh-prod-vpc) with CIDR 172.16.0.0/16
Created 4 subnets across 2 availability zones:
dipesh-prod-public-1 (172.16.1.0/24) in us-east-1a
dipesh-prod-public-2 (172.16.2.0/24) in us-east-1b
dipesh-prod-private-app-1 (172.16.3.0/24) in us-east-1a
dipesh-prod-private-db-1 (172.16.4.0/24) in us-east-1b
Created Internet Gateway for public subnet access
Created NAT Gateway for private subnet outbound access
Created public and private route tables with correct associations
Enabled VPC Flow Logs to CloudWatch for network monitoring

Security Layer:

Created KMS encryption key (dipesh-prod-key) for all data at rest
Created 3 tiered security groups:
dipesh-prod-alb-sg accepts HTTP and HTTPS from internet
dipesh-prod-app-sg accepts traffic from ALB only
dipesh-prod-db-sg accepts MySQL from app servers only
Configured AWS Backup with daily 35 day retention policy
Enabled GuardDuty AI protection plans for threat detection
Created production SNS alerts topic with confirmed subscription

